@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Obtener usuarios y productos para IDs válidos
# @name getUsers
GET {{baseUrl}}/users HTTP/1.1

###

# @name getProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/products HTTP/1.1

###

### POST toggle favorito (crear)
# @name toggle
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{getUsers.response.body.$.data[0].id}}",
  "productId": "{{getProducts.response.body.$.data[0].id}}"
}

###

### GET favoritos de un usuario
GET {{baseUrl}}/favorites?userId={{getUsers.response.body.$.data[0].id}} HTTP/1.1

###

### POST toggle favorito (eliminar — mismo body lo quita)
POST {{baseUrl}}/favorites HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{getUsers.response.body.$.data[0].id}}",
  "productId": "{{getProducts.response.body.$.data[0].id}}"
}
